<br>
Time to amend the treaties, or withdraw from them. Personally I would prefer to amend them but I am not married to the idea.<br>
<br>
We need nuclear powered spacecraft, and the sooner we have them the better. I realize systems like Orion are not perfect, but they are available. It will be a real downer if we need such a system and we don’t have it available. Extinction sucks.  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
